  "_anonymization_note": "Original example values across all node `examples` arrays have been replaced with synthetic placeholders to protect contractor, employee, and client confidentiality. The structural schema (47 nodes, edges, types, semantics) is unchanged from the version actually used in the §5.5 generative validation experiment.",
